dc_title_s: El Salvador basic demographic data from 2007 census
dc_description_s: Shapefile containing 2007 basic demographic data for El Salvador, including ages, relationships, and birthdates of household members, displayed at municipality level. The data were released by the Dirección General de Estadística y Censos (DIGESTYC) and sold by East View Geospatial.
dc_creator_sm: Dirección General de Estadística y Censos (DIGESTYC)
